title: Mexican Kidney Bean & Veggie Nachos with Charred Corn Salsa & Plant-Based Mayo
description: We turned the best things about nachos (the beans) into something irresistible and it’s all thanks to the
Mexican flavours and enchilada sauce. We've also added fresh corn salsa and a dollop of plant-based mayo
so you can enjoy an explosion of flavour with every bite.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

